Package miml.classifiers.miml.mimlTOmi

Class MIMLClassifierToMI

  • java.lang.Object
    • miml.classifiers.miml.MIMLClassifier
      • miml.classifiers.miml.mimlTOmi.MIMLClassifierToMI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IMIMLClassifier, IConfiguration, mulan.classifier.MultiLabelLearner
    public class MIMLClassifierToMI
extends MIMLClassifier

    Class implementing the transformation algorithm for MIML data to solve it with MI learning. For more information, see Zhou, Z. H., & Zhang, M. L. (2007). Multi-instance multi-label learning with application to scene classification. In Advances in neural information processing systems (pp. 1609-1616).

    Version:
    20180701
    Author:
    Alvaro A. Belmonte, Eva Gibaja, Amelia Zafra
